---
import { ArrowRight, Gauge, Rocket, ShieldCheck } from "lucide-react";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import sdLogo from "../assets/sd-logo-cropped.png";
---

<Layout
  title="Sawatzky Development | Premium Web Engineering"
  description="High-performance web engineering for local business. Astro-first builds for speed, security, and conversion."
>
  <section class="mx-auto w-full max-w-6xl px-4 pb-14 pt-14 sm:px-6 sm:pb-16 sm:pt-20 lg:px-8 lg:pt-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <p class="mb-4 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-sky-400/30 bg-sky-400/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium tracking-wide text-sky-200">
        <Rocket class="h-3.5 w-3.5" />
        Custom Websites Built Around Your Business
      </p>
      <h1 class="text-balance text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight text-white sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
        Your Website Should Bring You More Qualified Leads, Not More Friction.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-pretty text-base leading-relaxed text-zinc-300 sm:text-lg">
        I build bespoke, lightning-fast websites engineered around your offer, your market, and your growth goals, so your site becomes a sales asset instead of a brochure.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row">
        <a
          href="#portfolio"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-sky-300 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-950 transition hover:bg-sky-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-sky-100"
        >
          View the Performance Audit
          <ArrowRight class="h-4 w-4" />
        </a>
        <a
          href="#contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-sky-900/60 bg-slate-900/40 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-100 transition hover:border-sky-500/60 hover:bg-slate-900 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-sky-100"
        >
          Book a Consultation
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-sky-200/90">
        Plans start at <span class="text-white">$250 setup + $49/month</span>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="services" class="scroll-mt-28 mx-auto w-full max-w-6xl px-4 pb-16 sm:scroll-mt-32 sm:px-6 sm:pb-20 lg:px-8">
    <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-sky-800/60 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-slate-900 to-sky-950/40 p-6 sm:p-8 lg:p-10">
      <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-y-0 left-0 w-1 bg-sky-300/70"></div>
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-sky-400/30 bg-sky-400/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-sky-200">
        <Gauge class="h-3.5 w-3.5" />
        The Problem
      </div>
      <h2 class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-2xl font-semibold text-white sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl">
        Most Business Websites Look Fine but Fail to Convert.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-300 sm:text-base">
        Generic templates blur your positioning, slow down your pages, and make visitors work too hard to understand why they should choose you.
        If the message is unclear, good leads bounce.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-7">
        <a
          href="#portfolio"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-sky-900/60 bg-slate-900/40 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-100 transition hover:border-sky-500/60 hover:bg-slate-900"
        >
          Show Me the Real Cost
          <ArrowRight class="h-4 w-4" />
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="portfolio" class="scroll-mt-28 mx-auto w-full max-w-6xl px-4 pb-16 sm:scroll-mt-32 sm:px-6 sm:pb-20 lg:px-8">
    <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-cyan-800/60 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-cyan-950/20 to-slate-900 p-6 sm:p-8 lg:p-10">
      <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-1 bg-cyan-300/70"></div>
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-cyan-400/30 bg-cyan-400/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-cyan-200">
        <ShieldCheck class="h-3.5 w-3.5" />
        The Cost
      </div>
      <h2 class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-2xl font-semibold text-white sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl">
        DIY Seems Cheaper Until Your Time and Lost Leads Are Counted.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-300 sm:text-base">
        Every hour spent wrestling with platforms, plugins, or page builders is an hour not spent selling, serving clients, or growing revenue.
        The hidden cost of DIY is momentum.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-slate-800">
        <div class="grid gap-0 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <article class="border-b border-slate-800 bg-slate-950/40 p-5 sm:border-b-0 sm:border-r">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-200">DIY / Template Route</h3>
            <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-zinc-300">
              <li>- Slower launch, trial-and-error process</li>
              <li>- Performance and SEO often capped by platform</li>
              <li>- Ongoing maintenance stress on your team</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
          <article class="bg-slate-950/60 p-5">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-sky-200">With Sawatzky Development</h3>
            <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-zinc-200">
              <li>- Clear strategy, faster execution, less guesswork</li>
              <li>- Custom Astro build focused on speed and conversion</li>
              <li>- Managed setup so you stay focused on business</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-7">
        <a
          href="#contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-sky-300 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-950 transition hover:bg-sky-200"
        >
          Get the Faster Path
          <ArrowRight class="h-4 w-4" />
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="contact" class="scroll-mt-28 mx-auto w-full max-w-6xl px-4 pb-20 sm:scroll-mt-32 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-blue-800/60 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-950/30 via-slate-900 to-slate-900 p-6 sm:p-8 lg:p-10">
      <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-y-0 right-0 w-1 bg-blue-300/70"></div>
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-blue-400/30 bg-blue-400/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-blue-200">
        <Rocket class="h-3.5 w-3.5" />
        The Opportunity
      </div>
      <h2 class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-2xl font-semibold text-white sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl">
        Get a Custom Site Without the Typical Agency Price Shock.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-300 sm:text-base">
        The hybrid subscription model keeps this an easy yes: a lower setup fee, predictable monthly cost, and managed website care without you
        becoming the web team.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
        <article class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-950/40 p-5">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">The Starter</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold text-sky-200">$250 setup + $49/mo</p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-300">
            For businesses needing a fast, high-converting one-page site.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-zinc-400">Includes 30 minutes of monthly updates</p>
        </article>
        <article class="rounded-xl border border-sky-700/60 bg-slate-950/60 p-5 shadow-[0_0_0_1px_rgba(56,189,248,0.2)]">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">The Professional</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold text-sky-200">$500 setup + $79/mo</p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-200">
            For service businesses needing multi-page structure, stronger messaging, and portfolio/project galleries.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-zinc-400">Includes 60 minutes of monthly updates</p>
        </article>
        <article class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-950/40 p-5">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">The Growth</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold text-sky-200">$750+ setup + $125/mo</p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-300">
            For ecommerce or booking flows with Stripe integrations and conversion-focused custom functionality.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-zinc-400">Includes 120 minutes of monthly updates</p>
        </article>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-950/40 p-5">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-zinc-200">Every Monthly Plan Includes</h3>
        <ul class="mt-3 grid gap-2 text-sm text-zinc-300 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <li>- Enterprise hosting on Cloudflare edge</li>
          <li>- Security hardening and SSL management</li>
          <li>- Priority support and minor site improvements</li>
          <li>- Monthly update time scales by package tier</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-7 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row">
        <a
          href="mailto:hello@sawatzky.dev"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-sky-300 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-950 transition hover:bg-sky-200"
        >
          Book a Consultation
          <ArrowRight class="h-4 w-4" />
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://sawatzky.dev"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-sky-900/60 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-100 transition hover:border-sky-500/60 hover:bg-slate-800"
        >
          See Full Plan Details
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="border-t border-slate-800">
    <div class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-6xl flex-col gap-2 px-4 py-6 text-sm text-zinc-400 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="inline-flex items-center gap-2">
        <img src={sdLogo.src} alt="SD monogram" class="h-5 w-5 object-contain" loading="lazy" />
        Built with Astro in Spruce Grove, AB
      </p>
      <a href="https://sawatzky.dev" class="text-sky-200 underline-offset-4 hover:underline">sawatzky.dev</a>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>
